   <pb facs="2"/>
   <head>TYPOGRAPHVS
Lectori.</head>
   <p>HAbes, Lector, breviter &amp; perspicuè ex<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>posita,
quae G. <hi>Buchananus</hi> tyronibus
ad Poetices rudimenta censuit neces<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>saria.
Ille enim non doctrina modó sed judi<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>cio
vir incomparabilis nullam hinc ingenij
laudem (quā ex alijs scriptis literatorum om<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>nium
judicio satis amplam consequutus est)
affectare voluit: verum ad captum puerorum,
quibus solis haec scripta sunt, se totum accom<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>modavit.
Quod si tanto viro per occupatio<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>nes
&amp; graviora studia, licuisset reliquas Gram<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>maticae
partes, pari facilitate strictim percur<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>risse,
Deus bone, quanta inde utilitas studiosae
juventuti accessisset.</p>
   <closer>
      <signed>Rovertus Walde-graue</signed>
   </closer>
